title: "CodeCRDT: Real-time Collaborative Code Editing Platform"
abstract: "CodeCRDT is a real-time collaborative code editing platform powered by Conflict-free Replicated Data Types (CRDTs) and AI agents. It enables multiple developers to edit code simultaneously without conflicts, featuring integrated AI assistance for code generation, debugging, and optimization. The platform combines Monaco Editor with Yjs CRDT implementation, providing seamless synchronization across distributed sessions with sub-10ms latency for local operations."
